        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col">
                    <p class="display-3">How to Use PneumoTrack</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="container mt-4">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-12">
                    <p class="fs-5">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" fill="#0080ff" class="bi bi-chevron-right" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                          <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4.646 1.646a.5.5 0 0 1 .708 0l6 6a.5.5 0 0 1 0 .708l-6 6a.5.5 0 0 1-.708-.708L10.293 8 4.646 2.354a.5.5 0 0 1 0-.708z"/>
                        </svg>
                        On the home page, fill in the patient’s details including first name, last name, gender, and age. These details will appear on the report.
                    </p>
                    <p class="fs-5">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" fill="#0080ff" class="bi bi-chevron-right" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                          <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4.646 1.646a.5.5 0 0 1 .708 0l6 6a.5.5 0 0 1 0 .708l-6 6a.5.5 0 0 1-.708-.708L10.293 8 4.646 2.354a.5.5 0 0 1 0-.708z"/>
                        </svg>
                        Ensure you provide accurate information as it will be used to generate your medical report.
                    </p>
                    <p class="fs-5">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" fill="#0080ff" class="bi bi-chevron-right" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                          <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4.646 1.646a.5.5 0 0 1 .708 0l6 6a.5.5 0 0 1 0 .708l-6 6a.5.5 0 0 1-.708-.708L10.293 8 4.646 2.354a.5.5 0 0 1 0-.708z"/>
                        </svg>
                        Select "Yes" if you want to receive the report via email. Ensure your email is correct for successful delivery.
                    </p>
                    <p class="fs-5">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" fill="#0080ff" class="bi bi-chevron-right" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                          <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4.646 1.646a.5.5 0 0 1 .708 0l6 6a.5.5 0 0 1 0 .708l-6 6a.5.5 0 0 1-.708-.708L10.293 8 4.646 2.354a.5.5 0 0 1 0-.708z"/>
                        </svg>
                        After submitting the form, you will be directed to the result page. You should receive the report within 10-20 seconds.
                    </p>
                    <p class="fs-5">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" fill="#0080ff" class="bi bi-chevron-right" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                          <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4.646 1.646a.5.5 0 0 1 .708 0l6 6a.5.5 0 0 1 0 .708l-6 6a.5.5 0 0 1-.708-.708L10.293 8 4.646 2.354a.5.5 0 0 1 0-.708z"/>
                        </svg>
                        On the result page, view your Chest X-ray and the prediction result. The report will be available below the result for download and printing.
                    </p>
                    <p class="fs-5">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" fill="#0080ff" class="bi bi-chevron-right" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                          <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4.646 1.646a.5.5 0 0 1 .708 0l6 6a.5.5 0 0 1 0 .708l-6 6a.5.5 0 0 1-.708-.708L10.293 8 4.646 2.354a.5.5 0 0 1 0-.708z"/>
                        </svg>
                        If your result indicates pneumonia, please visit the nearest hospital immediately. Even if the result is normal but symptoms persist, consult a doctor.
                    </p>
                    <p class="fs-5">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" fill="#0080ff" class="bi bi-chevron-right" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                          <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4.646 1.646a.5.5 0 0 1 .708 0l6 6a.5.5 0 0 1 0 .708l-6 6a.5.5 0 0 1-.708-.708L10.293 8 4.646 2.354a.5.5 0 0 1 0-.708z"/>
                        </svg>
                        For more details on how PneumoTrack works, visit the ‘About’ page using the navigation bar.
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-danger fs-5">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" fill="red" class="bi bi-exclamation-triangle-fill" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                          <path d="M7.938 2.016a.13.13 0 0 1 .123 0l6.856 3.94c.078.045.123.129.123.22v7.568a.25.25 0 0 1-.123.22l-6.856 3.941a.13.13 0 0 1-.123 0l-6.856-3.94a.25.25 0 0 1-.123-.22V6.177a.25.25 0 0 1 .123-.22l6.856-3.941zM7 6v4h2V6H7zm0 5v1h2v-1H7z"/>
                        </svg>
                        Please upload only valid chest X-ray images. Non-chest X-ray images may lead to incorrect results.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
